{"tid":1782123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最近連登係咁吹一隻風叫勇武地下化。。","createTime":"2019-12-13T16:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T01:24:26.000Z","uid":311486,"like":60,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"49d5654a393da4f3ec5fd5fa29f8999c4fcb77c3","tid":1782123,"uid":311486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T16:40:51.000Z","msg":"最近，成日聽到有呼籲要勇武地下化、小隊快閃、靜靜雞贏。<br />\n<br />\n要「地下化」、要「快閃」，係為咗不被捕。<br />\n要「靜靜雞」，唔好周圍講夢境，都係為咗不被捕。<br />\n<br />\n過去行動，勇武會有哨兵、街坊師、車手、物資手足backup。但而家所謂嘅「地下化」同「小隊快閃」係近乎完全冇backup。俾狗咬仲會有人話送頭，僥倖得手亦有事後孔明講「我就係要呢啲」。<br />\n<br />\n試想像吓，當幾個勇武，black bloc哂，喺無預告下，突然出現喺五顏六色嘅人群當中，然後裝修/set rb，要識得點變法術，先可以逃過cctv同班藍絲嘅耳目，確保安全地換裝，離開現場？<br />\n<br />\n勇武為矛，和理為盾。有多啲人護住，便衣差佬出手嘅成本亦大增，而唔係差佬對手足3on3就可以拉人走。到時候手足唔好話望有人救，可能有人影到相幫手廣傳已經係萬幸；唔好彩嘅，俾人拉之餘，仲要受藍絲啲冷言冷語。<br />\n<br />\n勇和係命運共同體，唇亡齒寒。體制外抗爭嘅成本同風險都好大，需要嘅唔止係一句「不割」，然後將責任外判。更重要嘅係同行，喺行動上互相補位配合。所有人都需要進化。<br />\n<br />\n明白小隊嘅人越多越危險。但小隊除咗要有勇武，亦免不過要組織和理非做後勤支援。和理非們又準備好了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論。<br />\n<br />\n圖：Man僧<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/596896340490193/posts/1458411557671996?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F596896340490193%2Fposts%2F1458411557671996%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIJtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=2d4c59b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/596896340490193/posts/1458411557671996?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n唔係個個小隊都好似屠龍 v小隊咁，冇和理非back up真係好難做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b98d18e9d07f378f00381a6c8ca57e597dd124c3","tid":1782123,"uid":116568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T16:42:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cd7f78c19493883e0f0665ef16b6d255a470dd31","tid":1782123,"uid":181502,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T16:43:20.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"9ed0782657de6cb4931d3e04c1d97db05064086e","tid":1782123,"uid":73212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T16:43:53.000Z","msg":"對唔住，借個位宣傳一下。<br />\n<br />\n[ 國際戰線 ] 歐洲巡迴展覧團隊眾籌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1768712/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1768712/page/1</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cbd930b20583a3ecbc82c74836c955ab61dfa35d","tid":1782123,"uid":277888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T16:44:41.000Z","msg":"推唔郁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba2e4106622fa3b7482b29e598a7dda7ce629d4","tid":1782123,"uid":81236,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T16:44:45.000Z","msg":"勇武唔係應該地下化<br />\n<br />\n真正地下化既應該係班冷氣軍師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勇武要做既係be water<br />\n<br />\n一定要人多cover先安全<br />\n<br />\n唔打陣地戰等等就得"},{"pid":"97ea842ddbed2bc430071fc0cb204033b3909be9","tid":1782123,"uid":39796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T16:44:58.000Z","msg":"其實大家都係鳩講"},{"pid":"8dd70093d89053b1acd48731d6970a8be408b298","tid":1782123,"uid":330457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T16:45:10.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"76e2615d777776222b7d0f6ea7a837a1f35ed5a1","tid":1782123,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97ea842ddbed2bc430071fc0cb204033b3909be9","tid":1782123,"uid":39796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T16:44:58.000Z","msg":"其實大家都係鳩講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T16:46:31.000Z","msg":"鳩講但真係會有人信<br />\n<br />\n亦都會有和理非信，覺得起下化係岩"},{"pid":"aa9a9b7eb1a0b26974bdfa9c6d9249de0e78521d","tid":1782123,"uid":201605,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T16:48:03.000Z","msg":"邊個話地下化係要表露身份？<br />\n地下化就係要好似殺手咁，殺人於無形，你根本見唔到佢係邊，甚至唔需要喺現場<br />\n我諗你誤解左形式上點樣地下化"},{"pid":"ae462ddbf0265a934cf545d483